trans-unit.source: Represents a request to move focus to another control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en forespørsel om å flytte fokus til en annen kontroll.

trans-unit.source: This class is used as an input parameter for the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes som inndataparameter for den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A> method has a WPF framework-level override that provides a more practical implementation (<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), as well as a parallel implementation on <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> and <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A>metoden har en WPF framework nivå override som gir en mer praktisk implementering (<xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), og en parallell implementering på <xref:System.Windows.ContentElement>og <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement>.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkContentElement> </xref:System.Windows.ContentElement> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.MoveFocus%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.MoveFocus%2A>

trans-unit.source: You typically will set properties on TraversalRequest in order to customize the focusing behavior when you request that the focus be moved to another element.
trans-unit.target: Du vil vanligvis angi egenskaper for TraversalRequest for å tilpasse focusing virkemåten når du ber om at fokus flyttes til et annet element.

trans-unit.source: This class is also used as input parameters for the following methods: - <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, and implementations of that method that are used for interoperation (<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen brukes også som inndataparametere for følgende metoder:- <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, og implementeringer av denne metoden som brukes til bruken (<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The intended direction of the focus traversal, as a value of the enumeration.
trans-unit.target: Tiltenkte sorteringsretningen {traversering fokus som en verdi av opplistingen.

trans-unit.source: This property is read-only because the <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection> is a required input parameter of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest> class constructor.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er skrivebeskyttet fordi den <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>er et obligatorisk inndataparameter av den <xref:System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest>klassekonstruktør.</xref:System.Windows.Input.TraversalRequest> </xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>

trans-unit.source: One of the traversal direction enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Én av traversering retningen opplisting verdier.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether focus traversal has reached the end of child elements that can have focus.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om fokus traversering har nådd slutten av underordnede elementer som kan ha fokus.

trans-unit.source: Focusable elements are those elements where the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A> property is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Focusable elementer er elementene der den <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>

trans-unit.source: This parameter is primarily intended to communicate whether traversal using tab stops should wrap when calling the methods <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>,or.<xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSite.OnNoMoreTabStops%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Denne parameteren er primært ment å kommunisere om traversering ved hjelp av kategorien stopper skal brytes når du kaller metodene <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A>, eller.<xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSite.OnNoMoreTabStops%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSite.OnNoMoreTabStops%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you are passing focus to an object that implements <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink>, then specifying true for Wrapped will result in that `true` value being passed to the <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du sender fokus til et objekt som implementerer <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink>, angi true for Wrapped fører som `true` verdien som ble sendt til den <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>implementeringen.</xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if this traversal has reached the end of child elements that can have focus; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis denne traversering har nådd slutten av underordnede elementer som kan ha fokus. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
